                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item>
                           <label>
                              <locus>Front inside cover</locus>
                           </label>A printed note is pasted in: "197 Tezkireh as Shoara, Elegant Extracts from a numerous list of Ancient and Modern Persian Authors, Persian, very neatly written on variously tinted paper, 4to, in the original embossed gilt Persian binding, 3l. 3s. This volume is rarely to be met with in this country, and highly esteemed in the East".</item>
                        <item>
                           <locus>Inside Covers</locus>Various notes in pen and pencil relating to former ownership and transfer: "No. 15. Elegant Extracts", "S.2657", "£3.3", "5/27", "6/6/0".</item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
                  <bindingDesc>
                     <p>Original binding. Leather on pasteboard. Embossed with floral and figural designs and gilded.</p>
                     <decoNote type="other"/>
                  </bindingDesc>
